\c 2
\s UJesu usilisa umuntu oyisigoga
\p
\v 1 Njalo wabuya wangena eKapenawume\x + Mat. 9.1. Luka 5.17.\x* emva kwezinsuku\x + Mat. 26.61.\x*; kwasekuzwakala ukuthi usendlini\x + 3.19.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo kwahle kwabuthana abanengi, akwazabe kusaba lendawo ya\add bo\x + Joha. 21.25.\x*\add*, ngitsho langasemnyango; wasekhuluma ilizwi kubo.
\v 3 Basebesiza kuye, beletha owome umhlubulo, ethwelwe ngabane\x + Joha. 21.25.\x*.
\v 4 Babengelakusondela kuye ngenxa yexuku, bavula\x + Luka 5.19.\x* uphahla lapho ayekhona, bathi sebe\add lu\add*bhobozile behlisa ithala alele kulo owome umhlubulo\x + Gal. 4.15.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo uJesu ebona ukholo lwabo wathi kowome umhlubulo: Ndodana, izono zakho uzithethelelwe\x + Mat. 9.2.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa abanye bababhali ababehlezi lapho, banakana enhliziyweni zabo\x + Luka 3.15.\x*, \add bathi\add*:
\v 7 Ukhulumelani inhlamba enje lo? Ngubani ongathethelela izono ngaphandle koyedwa, uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 32.5. Isa. 43.25. Jobe 14.4.\x*?
\v 8 Njalo khonokho uJesu ekwazi emoyeni wakhe ukuthi babenakana njalo phakathi kwabo, wathi kubo: Linakanelani izinto lezi enhliziyweni zenu\x + Luka 3.15.\x*?
\v 9 Yikuphi okulula, ukuthi kowome umhlubulo: Izono \add zakho\add* uzithethelelwe\x + Mat. 9.2.\x*, kumbe ukuthi: Sukuma, uthathe icansi lakho, uhambe?
\v 10 Kodwa ukuze lazi ukuthi iNdodana yomuntu ilamandla okuthethelela izono emhlabeni (wathi kowome umhlubulo):
\v 11 Ngithi kuwe: Sukuma uthathe icansi lakho, uye endlini yakho.
\v 12 Njalo wahle wasukuma, wathatha icansi, waphuma phambi kwabo bonke; baze bamangala bonke\x + Luka 2.47.\x*, bamdumisa uNkulunkulu, besithi: Kasizange sikubone okunje.
\s Ukubizwa kukaLevi
\p
\v 13 Wasebuya esiya elwandle, ixuku lonke laselisiza kuye, wasebafundisa\x + 1.45.\x*.
\v 14 Wathi esedlula wabona uLevi okaAlfewu ehlezi endlini yokuthelisela, wasesithi kuye: Ngilandela. Wasesukuma wamlandela\x + Mat. 9.9.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Kwasekusithi ehlezi endlini yakhe, labathelisi abanengi lezoni bahlala ekudleni loJesu labafundi bakhe\x + Luka 5.29. Mat. 9.10.\x*; ngoba babebanengi, njalo bemlandela.
\v 16 Kwathi ababhali labaFarisi, bembona esidla labathelisi lezoni, bathi kubafundi bakhe: Kungani esidla enatha labathelisi lezoni?
\v 17 Kwathi uJesu esezwile wathi kubo: Abaphilileyo kabadingi melaphi, kodwa labo abagulayo. Kangizanga ukubiza abalungileyo, kodwa izoni zize ekuphendukeni.
\s Ukuzila ukudla
\p
\v 18 Njalo abafundi bakaJohane lababaFarisi babezila ukudla; basebesiza bathi kuye: Kungani abafundi bakaJohane lababaFarisi bezila ukudla, kodwa abafundi bakho bengazili ukudla\x + Mat. 9.14-17. Luka 5.33.\x*?
\v 19 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Amadodana endlu yomthimba angazila yini ukudla, umyeni eselawo? Angezile, ingqe ngesikhathi umyeni eselawo;
\v 20 kodwa zizafika insuku lapho umyeni azasuswa kuwo, njalo khona azazila ukudla ngalezonsuku\x + Luka 17.22.\x*.
\v 21 Futhi kakho othungela isichibi selembu elingakafinyeli esembathweni esidala; uba-ke kungenjalo okubekelweyo kudabuke kiso, okutsha kwesidala, kuqhele ukudabuka.
\v 22 Futhi kakho othela iwayini elitsha emigodleni emidala; uba-ke kungenjalo iwayini elitsha lidabula imigodla, lichitheke iwayini lemigodla yonakale; kodwa iwayini elitsha limele lifakwe emigodleni emitsha.
\s UJesu uchasisa umlayo wesabatha
\p
\v 23 Kwasekusithi edabula emasimini amabele ngesabatha\x + 2.23-26,28, Mat. 12.1-8. Luka 6.1-5.\x*, abafundi bakhe basebeqala ukukha izikhwebu behamba\x + Hlu. 17.8.\x*.
\v 24 AbaFarisi basebesithi kuye: Khangela, kungani besenza lokho okungavunyelwayo ngesabatha?
\v 25 Yena wasesithi kubo: Kalizange libale yini uDavida akwenzayo, mhla eswele, elambile, yena lababelaye?
\v 26 Ukuthi wayangena njani endlini kaNkulunkulu esikhathini uAbhiyatha engumpristi omkhulu\x + 1 Lan. 24.6. 2 Sam. 8.17. 1 Sam. 21.1.\x*, wadla izinkwa zokubukiswa ezingavunyelwa ukudliwa ngaphandle kwabapristi, wabanika lababelaye?
\v 27 Wasesithi kubo: Isabatha lenziwa ngenxa yomuntu, njalo umuntu ke\add nzi\add*wanga ngenxa yesabatha\x + Eks. 23.12. Dute. 5.14.\x*;
\v 28 ngakho iNdodana yomuntu iyiNkosi leyesabatha\x + Mat. 12.8.\x*.